  "title": "Busana Melayu",
  "description": "A pack that changes all armors into traditional Malay attires",
  "body": "<img alt=\"The Busana Melayu Logo\" src=\"https://imgur.com/BQiiNIc.png\"  width=\"600\" height=\"300\">\n\n# Busana Melayu | Malay Attire | بوسان ملايو\n<font size=\"5.5\">**Busana Melayu, a Malay-themed armor replacement resource pack created by flurrry**</font><br />\n\n---\n\n<font size=\"5\">**What does this project add? / Apa yang ditambahkan dalam projek ini?**</font><br />\n- All armor sets has now changed into traditional Malay attires!\n- Semua set zirah kini telah berubah menjadi busana Melayu tradisional!\n\n<font size=\"5\">**If you want the female variant, check out [this page](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/busana-melayu-fv/)!**</font><br />\n\n<font size=\"4\">**Give flurrry a follow on [Modrinth](https://modrinth.com/user/flryae) and [PlanetMinecraft](https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/flurrry/)!!!**</font><br />\n\n\n---\n<font size=\"6\">**Available Versions / Versi Tersedia**</font><br />\n\n| Minecraft Versions | Available? |\n| :------------------ | :------------: |\n| 1.21 (Tricky Trials Update)<br/>1.20 (Trails & Tales Update)<br />1.19 (Wild Update)<br />1.18 (Cave & Cliffs Update - Part II)<br />1.17 (Caves & Cliffs Update - Part I)<br />1.16 (Nether Update) | ✔️ |\n| 1.15 (Buzzy Bees Update)<br />1.14 (Village & Pillage Update)<br />1.13 (Update Aquatic) | ✔️ |\n| 1.12 (World of Color Update)<br />1.11 (Exploration Update) | ✔️ |\n| 1.10 (Frostburn Update)<br />1.9 (Combat Update)<br />1.8 (Bountiful Update)<br />1.7 (Update That Changed The World)  | ✔️ |\n|  Beta 1.7.3 | Soon!™ |\n\n---\n\n<a href=\"https://minecraft.wiki/w/Tutorials/Loading_a_resource_pack#Any_platform\"><img title=\"Resource Pack Installation Guide\" alt=\"Resource Pack Installation Guide\" src=\"https://imgur.com/xhaFOjc.png\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mcedisimelayu.gitbook.io/wiki/english/busana-melayu/changelog\"><img title=\"Busana Melayu Changelogs\" alt=\"Busana Melayu Changelogs\" src=\"https://imgur.com/tL4PD3X.png\"></a>\n\n<font size=\"5\"><b>Male Variant</b></font><br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/busana-melayu/\"><img title=\"Busana Melayu Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Busana Melayu Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_64h.png\"></a><br />\n<font size=\"5\"><b>Female Variant</b></font><br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/busana-melayu-fv/\"><img title=\"Busana Melayu Female Variant Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Busana Melayu Female Variant Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_64h.png\"></a><br />\n<font size=\"5\"><b>Bedrock Port</b></font><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/busana-melayu-bedrock-port\"><img title=\"Busana Melayu for Bedrock Edition Page\" alt=\"Busana Melayu for Bedrock Edition Page\" src=\"https://github.com/blryface/blurrybadges/blob/main/badges/64h/Avaliable%20On%20PMC.png?raw=true\"></a>\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary><font size=\"5\">Check out other MCEM packs! / Jom tengok pek MCEM lainnya!</font></summary>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/senjata-melayu\"><img title=\"Senjata Melayu Project Page\" alt=\"Senjata Melayu Project Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a2124449f1add505386260aa853fe5ffef4b33ff.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/senjata-busana-melayu-cit\"><img title=\"Senjata + Busana Melayu CIT Project Page\" alt=\"Senjata + Busana Melayu CIT Project Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6a24ca09e861212e4ee8ae933a5d4572c433eebe.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/peranggu-pahlawan/\"><img title=\"Peranggu Pahlawan Mod Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Peranggu Pahlawan Mod Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/43a4ccce41cea018c41eae3792d93218ba7fa341.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/bettermalay-language-pack\"><img title=\"BetterMalay Language Pack Project Page\" alt=\"BetterMalay Language Pack Project Page\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ONEKpmY.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/jawicraft-language-pack\"><img title=\"JawiCraft Language Pack Project Page\" alt=\"JawiCraft Language Pack Project Page\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SZVLler.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/moddedmalay-translation-pack/\"><img title=\"ModdedMalay Translation Pack Modrinth Page\" alt=\"ModdedMalay Translation Pack Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/76260a321fb0abf69bfe2a19780fba40e1354de5.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/lombina-englishlah-melayunya/\"><img title=\"Lombina: Englishlah & Melayunya Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Lombina: Englishlah & Melayunya Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/dda933f8c446636a631fb2b2b26e33513f21cc9a.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/lombina-april-fools/\"><img title=\"Lombina: April Fools Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Lombina: April Fools Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f64c4f6029459d7cd0b0f4bbfc7a9f0adaa49c67.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/lombina-edisi-movie/\"><img title=\"Lombina: Edisi Movie Modrinth Page\" alt=\"Lombina: Edisi Movie Modrinth Page\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3f0d3a52a68293467d94448a6444c0e990d12f49.png\"></a>\n</details>\n\n---\n<font size=\"6\">**Credits / Penghargaan**</font><br />\n\n| Credits / Penghargaan | Contributor / Penyumbang |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Original Creator, Designer | flurrry |\n| Maintainer, Bedrock Port | Muhammad Nuruddin (NuruddinPlays) |\n| Idea for the Female Variant | SaraNyan |\n| Extra Credits | chipurinn |\n\n---\n<img alt=\"The Minecraft: Edisi Melayu Logo\" src=\"https://imgur.com/0HxIaqK.png\"  width=\"600\" height=\"300\">\n\n<font size=\"5\">**Sebuah Projek Koleksi Pek Sumber Minecraft Bertemakan Melayu<br />A Malay-themed Minecraft Resource Pack Collection Project<br />سبواه ڤروجيک کوليکسي ڤيک سومبر ماءينکرف‌ت برتيماکن ملايو**</font>\n\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/LamanWebMCEM\"><img title=\"Official MCEM Website\" alt=\"Official MCEM Website\" src=\"https://imgur.com/cHpL4jz.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://mcedisimelayu.gitbook.io/wiki\"><img title=\"Official MCEM Wiki\" alt=\"Official MCEM Wiki\" src=\"https://imgur.com/bYJyjcA.png\"></a>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MCEdisiMelayu\"><img title=\"MCEM's Twitter/X\" alt=\"MCEM's Twitter/X\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/twitter-singular_64h.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/4zAYBXzuha\"><img title=\"MCEM's Discord Server\" alt=\"MCEM's Discord Server\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-plural_64h.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/NuruddinPlays\"><img title=\"NuruddinPlays' Redirect Site\" alt=\"NuruddinPlays' Redirect Site\" src=\"https://imgur.com/SOv8wjd.png\"></a>\n\n---\n<font size=\"6\">**Original Description**</font><br />\n<font size=\"5\">**English**</font><br />\nThis pack DOES NOT requires optifine finally\n\nThis pack contains traditional Malay clothing (Baju Melayu) as armor\\\nYou can dye leather armor to make colorful clothes\\\nYeah that's it that's the pack.\n\nThanks for visiting/downloading! Any suggestions would be greatly appreciated\n\n\n\n<font size=\"5\">**Malay**</font><br />\nPek ini tidak memerlukan optifine\n\nPek ini mengandungi Baju Melayu yang menggantikan armor\\\nLeather armor boleh di warnakan untuk membuat baju yg berwarna-warni\\\n<font size=\"1\">~~ok tu je tk tau nk ltk apa lgi~~</font><br />\n\n\nTerima kasih kerana melawat/memuat turun! Segala cadangan amat dihargai",
